OL,3,                                  Q "###
OL,4,C The Ministry of Food Standards hasG1/2
OL,5,C an "Harmonisation Decree" for all     
OL,6,C Prodmash No.12 labels. To comply with 
OL,7,C EU naming conventions, Xenograd's     
OL,8,C beloved "Borscht-Jam" is to be        
OL,9,C renamed effective immediately:        
OL,11,  BEET MARMALADE                        
OL,13,F The familiar profile of sweet ginger  
OL,14,F and almonds over a thick, deep beet   
OL,15,F base remains the same. THE LEADER has 
OL,16,F tasted the new product and approved  F
OL,17,F its vibrant red hue.                  
OL,19,F Goulash Gary reminds all citizens that
OL,20,F calling the spread by its "Old Name"  
OL,21,F is now a Minor Deviation.             
OL,24,ANext  BDuties   CReporting   FPurity   
