OL,1,MA]G  Marmalade Rename              Px}0
OL,2,                       k                
OL,3,                                  Q "###
OL,4,C New Beet Marmalade's recipe has   G2/2
OL,5,C been skilfully enhanced and now       
OL,6,C contains 0% cadmium and no phthalates.
OL,7,                                       F
OL,8,  SAME TASTE:C10% more ginger for extra 
OL,9,C             zing.                     
OL,11,  SAME COLOUR:CMatches the red of our   
OL,12,              Cpatriotic logo.          
OL,14,  SAME JAR:C  Highly versatile storage. 
OL,16,F "A name is just a word," Chief Judge  
OL,17,F Jessica said, "But the Beet is        
OL,18,F eternal."                             
OL,20,  SABRE sensors at Commissaries will    
OL,21,  monitor that citizens are using the   
OL,22,  authorised name "Beet Marmalade" at   
OL,23,  tills.                                
